{"word":"Censer","slug":"censer","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Censer</b> Used for offering incense<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=16&verse=12'>Lev 16:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=14'>Num 4:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=16&verse=7'>Num 16:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=16&verse=18'>Num 16:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=16&verse=46'>Num 16:46</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=8&verse=3'>Rev 8:3</a><br/> For the temple, made of gold<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=50'>1Ki 7:50</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=4&verse=22'>2Ch 4:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=9&verse=4'>Heb 9:4</a><br/> Those which Korah used were converted into plates<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=16&verse=39'>Num 16:39</a><br/> Used in idolatrous rites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=8&verse=11'>Eze 8:11</a><br/> Symbolic<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=8&verse=3'>Rev 8:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=8&verse=5'>Rev 8:5</a>"}]}